# zbase32

A human-oriented base-32 encoding.

## ğŸ›  Installing

## poetry

```
poetry add python-zbase32
```

## pip

```
pip install python-zbase32
```

## ğŸ“ Usage

```pycon
>>> import zbase32
>>> zbase32.encode(b"asdasd")
'cf3seamuco'
>>> zbase32.decode("cf3seamu")
b"asdas"
```

